{"tid":2013684,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[公投] 應否將重慶大廈納入黃圈？","createTime":"2020-05-12T12:37:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T16:13:42.000Z","uid":69696,"like":27,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"13e0c995828636a3795ba514e7679ad8257361a5","tid":2013684,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T12:37:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">正方論點：</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n正1：少數族裔都係香港人，因為香港人呢個身份係跨越種族，佢地生意受打擊時，都需要人地幫<br />\n正2：佢地係遊行時都有幫手、派物資，亦有參與部份遊行<br />\n正3：支那係民族主義同種族歧視既政體，所以少數族裔唔係招安對象。若果我地主動幫手，可以招攬一班忠實盟友<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">反方論點：</span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n反1：佢地冇積極發聲、參加同貼文宣<br />\n反2：該地有眾多回教徒，而黃圈經常以回教視為不潔既連豬做宣傳<br />\n反3：佢地未必想牽涉政治<br />\n反4：佢地飽受官方歧視，入黃圈只會增加佢地被黑警打壓既機會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反對"},{"pid":"b398eb369c8f457393cf40d139b20d3f3d24d774","tid":2013684,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T12:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7546f5bd60e67638828ecf1219911fd52cc8ac","tid":2013684,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T12:39:46.000Z","msg":"好多巴基佬親中"},{"pid":"7071a2e5dad80eb975e4e9627bb5836d2492e9b4","tid":2013684,"uid":221211,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T12:41:28.000Z","msg":"點解你有權決定人地藍定黃？"},{"pid":"8551b0f8dae8c87a3a00b1768fe12159a5b335f4","tid":2013684,"uid":131282,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7071a2e5dad80eb975e4e9627bb5836d2492e9b4","tid":2013684,"uid":221211,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T12:41:28.000Z","msg":"點解你有權決定人地藍定黃？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T12:42:47.000Z","msg":"你今日先問？😂呢度連登wor 比弱智上ga😂😂"},{"pid":"19f68dfff187dfd127be1b918a405ce3f3fc1